{"tid":722643,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU：安安靜靜的她才是真的她！","createTime":"2018-06-29T16:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T06:56:03.000Z","uid":34643,"like":30,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"32d010b020bb01dfa91827bf2df2aba559e0d4f1","tid":722643,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"IU從2013年之後開始轉型，嘗試性感造型，曲風變成復古爵士。20歲出頭的年紀放棄了國民妹妹的可愛人設，一方面是事故導致，另一方面也可以看出她對自己未來的規劃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://78.media.tumblr.com/0ce6166678121a3b6992ffeb830b34e1/tumblr_n7s6aibnXL1rlzlwyo7_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F78.media.tumblr.com%2F0ce6166678121a3b6992ffeb830b34e1%2Ftumblr_n7s6aibnXL1rlzlwyo7_1280.jpg&h=7a8cfe92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n她不活潑，不覺得自己可愛，國民妹妹稱號在給她帶來巨大人氣的同時，也讓她不得不戴上面具。早期綜藝裡她總是嘰嘰喳喳說話的那個，反觀2017的 孝利的民宿，她總是發呆，不多說話，這才是真的她。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m.wanhuajing.com/pic/1602/0111/131487/9_500_681.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.wanhuajing.com%2Fpic%2F1602%2F0111%2F131487%2F9_500_681.jpg&h=a9ce00d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n她看很多書和電影，在我眼裡是真正的文青。書單裡包括陀思妥耶夫斯基，伍爾芙，太宰治等等，光粉絲問到的都有幾十本。歌詞裡也提到了甜橙樹，達洛維夫人等。這些書讓她思想非常成熟，也讓她有了作詞的積累。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bfeb342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fbfeb342.jpg&h=df39c629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為作詞人和專輯制作人，不可避免地要通過作品表達自己的想法，展示自己的精神世界。從這個角度來看，如果她有人設，人設是很難保持的。她本身也不想再用人設束縛自己，可以看到在孝利的民宿裡，她采取的是一種 無為 的態度，並沒有主動塑造積極的形像。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.clien.net/web/api/file/F01/4324360/77af2d1fa0f340659bf.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.clien.net%2Fweb%2Fapi%2Ffile%2FF01%2F4324360%2F77af2d1fa0f340659bf.JPG&h=ee1f9bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n優秀是她的天賦和努力帶來的，私底下她到底是什麼樣子我不了解，但是能讓周圍所有的前輩贊不絕口，她也不可能是什麼都不懂的白蓮花，她現在就是把自己的事情做到最好 ，我永遠相信她。她特別清楚自己要干什麼，說不擇手段我覺得沒到那程度，但是她自己的野心從來都沒藏著掖著，（當然團隊給她什麼設定另說），也非常清楚怎麼發揮自身優勢，知道怎麼樣迎合市場。"},{"pid":"6b58468f37fd9323578abcb6718ca1cd230288e5","tid":722643,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:12:09.000Z","msg":"山神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db1ee488153c81178b492a427fd4c2e82a7a649","tid":722643,"uid":59669,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:15:45.000Z","msg":"唔帶bra飛釘的她才是真的她<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dab90ff53ed9fa805fceb5476e843696e14033a","tid":722643,"uid":143667,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1db1ee488153c81178b492a427fd4c2e82a7a649","tid":722643,"uid":59669,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:15:45.000Z","msg":"唔帶bra飛釘的她才是真的她<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:23:07.000Z","msg":"同銀赫一齊先係真的她<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b839a5018b752c0ade23e4f0f015698e945dc8cd","tid":722643,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddf6c3873a57129e28d2d01395a2abb6b739ee7","tid":722643,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:43:24.000Z","msg":"佢一定好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05d248255ebd66e09a84e47f93d0ada4d97247f1","tid":722643,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T01:47:24.000Z","msg":"腳好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85dcbeb38249518de8937bb8543d85857dff7942","tid":722643,"uid":72076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T01:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/094658_fe9acf9a6c1132a0240ca878d21b1ee4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https